content:
Enable your sales reps or supervisors to choose a picklist option during a store visit for comparison with the target value. Configure the picklist values for a visit assessment task to help your users measure store performance more flexibly.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions where Consumer Goods Cloud is enabled.

How: Use Assessment Indicator Defined Value to configure the picklist options for an Assessment Indicator Definition of an assessment task. Provide a target value in Assessment Indicator Value by associating the Retail Store KPI with the Assessment Indicator Defined Values.
title: Easily Capture Store-Related Data
